window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>WHEN HEARTS BREAK, BODIES DROP...</p> <p>This collection of romantic thrillers proves one thing: some hearts are better left unbroken.</p> <p>From twisted love triangles to forbidden affairs, each story unearths the chaos that erupts when heartbreak push women past their limits.</p> <p>Desire becomes a death sentence. Lies are laced with lust. And love comes with a body count.</p> <p>These three stories are perfect for fans of messy love, dangerous games, and Black women who refuse to go down without a fight.</p>"; 
